trans-unit.source: You should not use this enumeration; it is not used by the .NET Framework remoting infrastructure.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Metadata.SoapTypeAttribute.XmlFieldOrder%2A> property of the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Metadata.SoapTypeAttribute> class gets or sets a value of type XmlFieldOrderOption.
